T1  - Corporate spinoffs and information asymmetry between investors
AU  - Huson, Mark R
AU  - MacKinnon, Gregory
JO  - Journal of Corporate Finance
VL  - 9
IS  - 4
SP  - 481
EP  - 503
PY  - 2003
DA  - 2003/09/01/
