T1  - The impact of informed trading on dividend signaling: a theoretical and empirical examination
AU  - Fuller, Kathleen P.
JO  - Journal of Corporate Finance
VL  - 9
IS  - 4
SP  - 385
EP  - 407
PY  - 2003
DA  - 2003/09/01/
T2  - Market Microstructure and Corporate Finance
